                    <button type="button" id="dncSlipCnConfirmBtn" onclick="dncSlipCreditNoteConfirm()" style="background:#7c3aed; color:#fff; border:0; padding:10px 18px; border-radius:6px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; font-weight:600;">💰 ยืนยันออก Credit Note</button>
